Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy made a raid on the Navy HQ to rescue \Nhis brother, Ace who was to be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his struggle ended in vain \Nas the war came to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is really dead, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy and Ace! The Story \Nof How the Brothers Met!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The War of the Best in Marineford \Nleft a scar in many people's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 years ago, in the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a small village called Windmill \NVillage where people lived peacefully
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but not far from it was Mt. Corvo \Nwhere people seldom stepped foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the strong could survive there and \Nthe weak who entered were doomed to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is, grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the King of the Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me... Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of eating the Devil \NFruit, you're talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Both you and Ace have to become
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:24.88,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MONKEY D. GARP [10 YEARS AGO]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the strongest Navy soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:29.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MONKEY D. LUFFY [10 YEARS AGO]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is rubber but why is it painful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to leave \Nyou in the Windmill Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things, you like \Npirates?! What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make friends \Nwith "Red-Haired" Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a strong man like Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!! Whoever you are, \Ndo you wanna get killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Garp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:17.98,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CURLY DADAN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:21.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A MOUNTAIN BANDIT: DOGRA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A MOUNTAIN BANDIT: MAGRA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break! Please, \Nyou gotta have mercy on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is 10 years old now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, already? How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't handle him anymore! \NYou have to take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Putting that aside...\N--Don't put it aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy, say "hi" to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Garp's... I mean, Garp-san's grandson?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, Here's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna spend all your \Nlife in prison or raise him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many crimes you \Ncommitted that I've overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't wanna get arrested but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I think that maybe it's better \Nto be in prison than take care of Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you want us to look after your \Ngrandson, too? I bet he's also a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crappy shack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! Ugh, spit! Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say "sorry"! It's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you back, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:05.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,PORTGAS D. ACE [10 YEARS AGO]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say "sorry"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, this is Ace. He's \N3 years older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna live here with them from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You can't just do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it decided?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all from me. I'll \Nstop by when I have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Um... What about some child support?\N--Put it on my bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is not a bar...\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're always welcome!\N--Boss, we can't take care of one more kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up! Let's just eat first! Fix it!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say "sorry"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this hat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your money or I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell your parents \Nto bring some money here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grandpa is my only...\N--That's fine. What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this kid...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna live here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why did you accept?!\N--This is not a day-care!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss has no guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give it to me, fool!\N--It's my meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You already ate!\N--I want more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna give in to young people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:10:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You got to share!\N--It's a dog-eat-dog world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His arm stretches!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn to wash dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have some more, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know where you are now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a den of the Dadan family, \Nmountain bandits that rule Mt. Corvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain bandits? I hate mountain bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you little shit! We're \Nannoyed by having a kid like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna stay here, that's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away and die like a dog somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna have that meat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all from a bison that Ace brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave us a cut of the \Ntake so everybody can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mountain bandits' world is rough sailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna have to work \Npretty hard from tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning, laundry, polishing \Nshoes and weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,burglary, robbery, fraud, and murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, you can't tell \NGarp what we make you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One bowl of rice and one \Nglass of water for a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can guarantee you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta get everything else by \Nyourself and grow up on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Okay"?! Why don't you cry or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine because grandpa \Nthrew me into a jungle once
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there was water to drink and frogs, \Nsnakes, and mushrooms to eat in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I'll become a pirate someday so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I must be strong like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss!\N--Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say "pirate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? He's too tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't wanna \Ntake care of Garp's grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Luffy! I'm not mad \Nabout you spitting on me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only spilled some booze on me. \NIt's nothing worth getting mad over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing worth getting mad \Nover. Let's become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ace is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, did you come back alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Luffy? I thought \Nthat you were with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool, where is he and what is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are dead if Garp finds out about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss must be pretty worried I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get hold of yourself, boss!\N--What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's not good that we \Nlost him on the first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares! if he dies, he dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp is gonna kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, why should we \Nlook after Garp's grandson?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not nannies! He has to \Ntake care of his own grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why don't you say it to him?\N--You have a problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Gold Roger had a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I know what'd happen to him! \NHe'd get his head cut off for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear from him as he dies:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry I was born! I'm \Njust a piece of trash!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already giving up on Ace, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if he dies or not. I'll \Njust tell Garp it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that "the devil's \Nchildren have the devil's luck"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the devil's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Government finds out about this, \Nwhat do you think they'd do to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're drinking too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.89,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE WEEK LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One week later...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Boss Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:17:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You!\N--Luffy came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You're alive! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy. Where were you \Nand what were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been chased by wolves \Nat the bottom of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing at \Nthe bottom of the valley?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Anyway, it's nice that you're okay.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not okay! The pest came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go to bed tonight? \NYou gotta work from tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna go somewhere today, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you! Let's become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! He's going after Ace again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You gotta do chores around the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit! You're out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bring him back right now!\N--Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Let's become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 8th day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bring him back!\N--Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 days have passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--He's gone already...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept going after Ace and losing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it went on everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 month...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 months...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter if it rained and was windy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy kept going after Ace desperately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is chasing Ace again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does he never learn after \Ngetting hurt so many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He has to stop making me worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way! Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bee-hive fell on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's coming \Nthis far. He's so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I lost him again! Ace runs so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the beast of Mt. \NCorvo! No one can beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he not running?! It's gonna eat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel weak at the knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Luffy had been chasing Ace for 3 \Nmonths with cuts and bruises all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Discarded junk lies around everywhere, \Nand smoke fills the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gray Terminal, a town of outlaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace once took charge of the thugs here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,amassing funds in order to \Nbecome a pirate someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with one other friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Here Comes Sabo! The Boy \Nat the Gray Terminal!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
